    "The next two sections describe our strategies of removing false positives and merging aliases for phases and properties given the specific characteristics of their text descriptions.",
    "Those strategies, while developed on the aluminum system, are applicable to other systems with minimal modification.",
    "PhasesAggregation and cleaning of phase entities was performed using a series of filters to remove, alter towards a unified format, and merge entities.",
    "The first step of phase name aggregation removed stop-words and modified the entities towards a unified format of phase and property representations.",
    "We distinguished two types of stop-words."
